title: Another Round of Milestone Closings
body:
Now that .NET 5 and VS 16.8 are released, is it possible to close out older milestones?

https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/milestones

- .NET 5
- MSBuild 16.7 Preview 4
- MSBuild 16.7
- MSBuild 16.8 Preview  1
- MSBuild 16.8 Preview  2
- 16.8
